@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/v1/api/reading-service
@collectionUrl = http://localhost:8080/v1/api/collections

# ===========================================
# HƯỚNG DẪN SỬ DỤNG:
# 1. Thay các giá trị {{collectionId}}, {{paperId}}, {{userId}} bằng IDs thực tế (đã encoded)
# 2. Chạy các request theo thứ tự từ trên xuống
# 3. Copy IDs từ response để dùng cho các request tiếp theo
# ===========================================

# ===========================================
# STEP 1: Lấy dữ liệu test (Collections, Papers, Users)
# ===========================================

### 1.1. Lấy danh sách Collections (để lấy collectionId)
GET {{collectionUrl}}?page=0&size=10
Accept: application/json

### 1.2. Lấy Collection by ID (thay {{collectionId}} bằng ID từ response trên)
# @collectionId = YjNjZGU2YTUtYWYyYi00ZDJjLTljYWYtN2UxODY3ZDY3OWI4
# GET {{collectionUrl}}/{{collectionId}}
# Accept: application/json

# ===========================================
# STEP 2: Tạo Workflows để có dữ liệu test
# ===========================================

### 2.1. Create Workflow 1 (User 1 - Paper 1)
# Thay {{collectionId}}, {{paperId}}, {{userId}} bằng IDs đã encoded
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "collectionId": "{{collectionId}}",
  "paperId": "{{paperId}}",
  "usersid": "{{userId}}"
}

### 2.2. Update Progress cho Workflow 1
PUT {{baseUrl}}/workflows/progress
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "collectionId": "{{collectionId}}",
  "paperId": "{{paperId}}",
  "usersid": "{{userId}}",
  "lastPage": 15,
  "progress": 45
}

### 2.3. Update Status cho Workflow 1
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/workflows/status
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "collectionId": "{{collectionId}}",
  "paperId": "{{paperId}}",
  "usersid": "{{userId}}",
  "status": "reading"
}

### 2.4. Create Workflow 2 (User 1 - Paper 2) - Để test với nhiều papers
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "collectionId": "{{collectionId}}",
  "paperId": "{{paperId2}}",
  "usersid": "{{userId}}"
}

### 2.5. Update Progress cho Workflow 2 (finished)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/workflows/progress
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "collectionId": "{{collectionId}}",
  "paperId": "{{paperId2}}",
  "usersid": "{{userId}}",
  "lastPage": 50,
  "progress": 100
}

### 2.6. Create Workflow 3 (User 2 - Paper 1) - Để test với nhiều users
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "collectionId": "{{collectionId}}",
  "paperId": "{{paperId}}",
  "usersid": "{{userId2}}"
}

### 2.7. Update Progress cho Workflow 3
PUT {{baseUrl}}/workflows/progress
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "collectionId": "{{collectionId}}",
  "paperId": "{{paperId}}",
  "usersid": "{{userId2}}",
  "lastPage": 30,
  "progress": 60
}

# ===========================================
# STEP 3: Test Progress Tracking APIs
# ===========================================

### 3.1. Get Collection Progress Statistics (Dashboard for PI)
# Endpoint chính để PI xem tổng quan tiến độ team
GET {{baseUrl}}/progress/collection/{{collectionId}}
Accept: application/json

### 3.2. Get Team Member Progress (User 1)
# Xem tiến độ của một thành viên cụ thể trong collection
GET {{baseUrl}}/progress/collection/{{collectionId}}/member/{{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### 3.3. Get Team Member Progress (User 2)
GET {{baseUrl}}/progress/collection/{{collectionId}}/member/{{userId2}}
Accept: application/json

### 3.4. Get Paper Progress in Collection (Paper 1)
# Xem tất cả team members đang đọc paper này như thế nào
GET {{baseUrl}}/progress/collection/{{collectionId}}/paper/{{paperId}}
Accept: application/json

### 3.5. Get Paper Progress in Collection (Paper 2)
GET {{baseUrl}}/progress/collection/{{collectionId}}/paper/{{paperId2}}
Accept: application/json

# ===========================================
# STEP 4: Test Workflows by Collection APIs
# ===========================================

### 4.1. Get All Workflows by Collection
# Lấy tất cả workflows trong collection
GET {{baseUrl}}/workflows/collection/{{collectionId}}
Accept: application/json

### 4.2. Get Workflows by Collection - Filter by Status: unread
GET {{baseUrl}}/workflows/collection/{{collectionId}}?status=unread
Accept: application/json

### 4.3. Get Workflows by Collection - Filter by Status: reading
GET {{baseUrl}}/workflows/collection/{{collectionId}}?status=reading
Accept: application/json

### 4.4. Get Workflows by Collection - Filter by Status: finished
GET {{baseUrl}}/workflows/collection/{{collectionId}}?status=finished
Accept: application/json

# ===========================================
# STEP 5: Test Edge Cases
# ===========================================

### 5.1. Get Collection Progress - Empty Collection (không có workflows)
# Thử với collectionId khác chưa có workflows
GET {{baseUrl}}/progress/collection/{{emptyCollectionId}}
Accept: application/json

### 5.2. Get Team Member Progress - User chưa có workflows
GET {{baseUrl}}/progress/collection/{{collectionId}}/member/{{newUserId}}
Accept: application/json

### 5.3. Get Paper Progress - Paper chưa có ai đọc
GET {{baseUrl}}/progress/collection/{{collectionId}}/paper/{{newPaperId}}
Accept: application/json

# ===========================================
# STEP 6: Test với các scenarios khác
# ===========================================

### 6.1. Update Progress để test auto-update status to "finished"
# Khi progress >= 100, status sẽ tự động chuyển thành "finished"
PUT {{baseUrl}}/workflows/progress
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "collectionId": "{{collectionId}}",
  "paperId": "{{paperId}}",
  "usersid": "{{userId}}",
  "lastPage": 100,
  "progress": 100
}

### 6.2. Verify status đã chuyển thành "finished"
GET {{baseUrl}}/workflows/collection/{{collectionId}}?status=finished
Accept: application/json

### 6.3. Get Collection Progress sau khi update
# Kiểm tra finishedCount đã tăng chưa
GET {{baseUrl}}/progress/collection/{{collectionId}}
Accept: application/json

# ===========================================
# NOTES:
# - Tất cả IDs phải được encode (Base64 URL-safe) trước khi gửi
# - Response format: { "success": true, "data": {...}, "message": "..." }
# - Status values: "unread", "reading", "finished"
# - Progress: 0-100 (integer)
# ===========================================

















